{"tid":536620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政治炸彈或累建制選情","createTime":"2018-01-22T03:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T13:46:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ecc8b4ebaa8d3522850883933e9e98ec5cf272","tid":536620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180122/20282205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180122%2F20282205&d=5a%2FMorWabTkAx6%2F7fnF3BW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=29de8447\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180122%2F20282205&h=7a4b3755\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180122/20282205</a><br />\n<br />\n政治炸彈或累建制選情<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】<br />\n立會3.11補選大戰當前，建制派原以為可以趁民主派「分裂」搶灘之際，特區政府卻突然拋出「政治炸彈」。新任律政司司長鄭若驊的僭建風波懸疑未解，上周政圈更有消息指，僭建風波或有續聞，有學者分析鄭若驊昨首到電台預告正跟進其他物業有否僭建，料是提早回應為事件降溫，免波及建制派選情。<br />\n<br />\n其實立會司法事務委員會曾邀請鄭若驊出席今天會議但被鄭拒絕，最快要下月底才到立會回應，據知建制派怨聲載道，指若臨近選舉才再「爆大鑊」，選情肯定嚴重受損。結果鄭昨早出席電台節目，率先提及正跟進名下其他物業有否僭建，似有意盡早拆彈。<br />\n<br />\n理大社會政策研究中心主任鍾劍華指，建制派為免鄭若驊僭建風波影響補選選情，大部份參選人過去都甚少直接評論事件，「都知道要避得就避」。鍾認為鄭試圖進一步解釋，並暗示可能還有其他物業有僭建問題，是想趁現時距離3.11補選仍有個多月，試圖降溫減低建制派壓力。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180122/large/0121hing10041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180122%2Flarge%2F0121hing10041.jpg&h=060fc63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭若驊<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t首上電台受訪七度致歉<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t鄭兼職仲裁　拒談是否涉財團<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t隔閘接請願信<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t早上受訪拒交代　深夜發稿鄭若驊再有物業三非法改裝<br />\n頭條 5小時前"},{"pid":"d2bce14eecf0753231e0c72038973feeb0433945","tid":536620,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"次次出呢D 新聞我都覺得好戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n屌你香港人係選舉前出事先覺得拖累到?<br />\n以前做嗰啲唔撚會拖累嘅"},{"pid":"43a892e267b7ce542dd3429f538912d7d0fd882a","tid":536620,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2bce14eecf0753231e0c72038973feeb0433945","tid":536620,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"次次出呢D 新聞我都覺得好戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n屌你香港人係選舉前出事先覺得拖累到?<br />\n以前做嗰啲唔撚會拖累嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"中產會上連登咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪當連登=香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d340e401bba750935f87474068939ce91bdbd32","tid":536620,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n大陸話屎都好食好有益，藍絲一樣撐"},{"pid":"65c394672a2066f8efdb91481eb05c511253be09","tid":536620,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"派錢即刻叫晒識既人投建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正垃圾會都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bda33a9782d3edebdeb8953d724d22fbeddb7d8","tid":536620,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43a892e267b7ce542dd3429f538912d7d0fd882a","tid":536620,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2bce14eecf0753231e0c72038973feeb0433945","tid":536620,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"次次出呢D 新聞我都覺得好戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n